description: TehKu Tea Dear friends of TehKu,  In an unfortunate turn of events; the property owner and management agency chose to terminate our lease for the TehKu Tea.  In accordance with the contract, we have until July the 31st to vacate the premises. With such a short notice, it is impossible to relocate the entire operations to a suitable location.   For now, the plan is to stay open and reduce inventory until July 23.  The following two weeks will be needed to move equipment, furniture, etc. Obviously, closing the store this abruptly impacts many people; our patrons (many of whom have become close friends through the 11+ years we have been open); the dedicated staff and the City of Dublin (losing a destination stop).   I am hopeful to be able to continue to provide quality tea to our loyal customers and am exploring ways to do that in the near- and long-term.  You can continue to contact us through Facebook or email: Inggrie@tehku.com.  I appreciate your support and welcome ideas that you may have in how we can make this transition as smooth as possible. I would love to stay in touch with everyone, please stop by and leave me your contact information so we can stay connected and keep you posted on our next move or email me your contact info.  I am having a party on 7/8 (RSVP only) and last open house 7/15, please stop by if you can.  With deepest regret,  Inggrie Shelly Collier Quillin Nikki Thomas Jenni Thomas Falkenheim
